    description "Better stacking, labeling and preservation increase practical reserve capacity."
    category PRODUCTION
    layout_order 50
    research_time 18
    cost PAPER 16
    cost PLANKS 20
    modifier SupplyCapacity multiplier 1.10
    modifier BuildTime multiplier 0.94 building StorageBuilding
end


